		</a>
		<a class="arrow" href="#" onclick="textSize('decrease'); return false;" rel="nofollow">
			<img src="/web/20100203214510im_/http://www.courant.com/hive/images/icons/atools-downarrow.gif" alt="decrease text size" class="arrow-img"/>
